RawLine: TNPC_60076411,是我委託{color=#FF0000}馬記貨行{/color}的人送來的。我才剛接完單，正巧貨行就送我需要的貨來了。我也沒想太多，反正剛好有貨我就用了。,是我委托{color=#FF0000}马记货行{/color}的人送来的。我才刚接完单，正巧货行就送我需要的货来了。我也没想太多，反正刚好有货我就用了。

Items.mt: I commissioned the people from Ma Ji's goods store to send it to me. I just took the order, and it just so happened that the goods company sent me the goods I needed. I didn't think too much about it, but it just happened to be in stock, so I used it.
